{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"818af0ff-ebc8-410b-9d7f-3a2702633ac3","content":"The template is **not quite ready** to publish. Here are the issues:\n\n**Missing required field:**\n- `$schema` — recommended for validation/IntelliSense (e.g., `\"$schema\": \"http://json.schemastore.org/template\"`)\n\n**Missing recommended fields:**\n- `groupIdentity` — needed if you plan multiple language/framework variants\n- `precedence` — helps NuGet resolve version ordering\n- `preferNameDirectory` — controls output folder behavior\n- `description` — important for discoverability on NuGet\n\n**Other concerns:**\n1. No `defaultName` specified (falls back to the directory name on `dotnet new`)\n2. The `sourceName` replacement is fine, but consider adding `\"preferDefaultName\": true`\n3. `classifications` are sparse — adding more tags (e.g., \"ASP.NET Core\") improves search visibility\n\n**Minimum fix to be publish-ready:** add a `description` field and the `$schema` reference. Everything else is optional but recommended for a polished NuGet listing.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"318e1546-cc57-45c9-b4bc-9d131b43f4cb","outputTokens":244,"requestId":"D006:156E46:14233B8:16A4520:69F94146"},"id":"16e6c1a2-b482-48ea-82e4-c496157464f7","timestamp":"2026-05-05T01:01:02.573Z","parentId":"2bbcb55e-b824-4a17-97bd-a7bff8411282"}
